title: 10/10: Trade Talk, Regulators, Fantasy Feud, PHI-NYG (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Fun show today as we give you some Buy Low (4:00) and Sell High (6:35) candidates. See if you can get Alvin Kamara at a low cost, and is Eric Ebron a sell or a hold? Within this discussion, we tell you which early-round RBs (8:15) are no longer buy low candidates and are simply busts ... NFL news (22:55), redrafting the first round as if the season started today (26:20), Fantasy Regulators Part One (32:25) and a PHI-NYG (36:30) preview. What do we do with those PHI RBs? ... Let's play the Fantasy Feud (44:35)! Jamey and Heath square off in an ugly battle. Then we grade your trades (53:16) and finish up with Fantasy Regulators Part Two (55:06) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
